refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;
result
PostgreSQL Large Object (LOB) Ressource, die von pg_lo_open zurückgegeben wurde.

  &reftitle.examples;



    pg_lo_close Beispiel


<?php
   $database = pg_connect("dbname=jacarta");
   pg_query($database, "begin");
   $oid = pg_lo_create($database);
   echo "$oid\n";
   $handle = pg_lo_open($database, $oid, "w");
   echo "$handle\n";
   pg_lo_write($handle, "Daten fuer das Large Object");
   pg_lo_close($handle);
   pg_query($database, "commit");
?>
